	<h1 class="title">随难民迁徙：翻过铁丝网涌进匈牙利之后，难民们不得不转向德国 | 难民危机是怎么回事 八</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Anemona Hartocollis</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-07 10:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15706/medium/15706.jpg?1444147343" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


